missionEventData.data1: During our attack on the Mugaari/Rebel weapons area, the Rebels launched a raid on Outpost D-34.  It fell to the Rebels despite a valiant fight.  The Rebel terrorists are in the process of looting the station for any arms or equipment they can steal.  Our objective for this mission is to retake the Outpost, recovering as much stolen material as we can.
Alpha 1, two Rebel transports are launching from the station. Don't let them reach the jump point!
Warning! Rebel fighters are jumping in from the edge of the system to protect their transports.
Two more rebel transports are launching. Ensure that no imperial equipment falls into Rebel hands!
More rebel ships are jumping in. X-Wing class!
Well done Alpha 1, we're launching a transport to capture the station. Provide cover.
Rebel ships exiting hyperspace. Don't let them hit the transport.
Well done. Commscan reports that the rebel cruiser at the edge of the system is withdrawing. The station is ours!
Return to the Fogger for debriefing.
Alpha 1 focus on those transports. Alpha 2, 3, and 4 engage those Y-Wings.
Same as before, Alpha 1 focus on those transports. Alpha 2, 3, and 4 engage those X-Wings.
